title: [LFT] Master Adc main
body:
Hello, 

I am currently looking for a 5's Team that wants to have fun and climb.  Please be Diamond or above.  I am a adc main and master in solo/duo queue.  Please add either this account or protoyns [I am on "protoyns" 99% of the time].

replies.body: I have 4 members currently including myself that are diamond +, i have added you on both account. please get back to me if you are keen. :)
